data.description:
2 MASTER SUITES! COMPLETE RENOVATION of $196K in 2019  GORGEOUS Home in the highly sought after
RISD neighborhood. Walk through Beautiful Front Door and Entry into Large Open Floor Plan perfect for Entertaining! Natural light floods through
Double French Doors and windows of this Charming Family Room with magnificent flooring, 2 ceiling fans, and fireplace with Shiplap! 
Enjoy the Exceptional Kitchen with Spacious 4 x 9.5 ft.butcher block island, additional seating, custom storage, custom cabinets, under mount lighting, Granite Countertops, High End Appliances and Farmhouse Sink! Separate Masters allow for privacy at each end of the house. Enjoy a soaking tub, glass shower, beautiful tile, walk in closets and Barn doors, and pool. Updates include: A C, Heating, Impact Resistant Roof, New Electrical Box, Double Paned Windows and Doors, Wooden Fence, Security System, Appliances, Paint, Flooring, Lighting, Foundation. See Documents for more Updates. This MUST SEE home won't last long.
